      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GREAT CHAT (7) has a strong winning strike-rate here with two wins and a placing from four tries. Below best last time at this track (30.05) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 5 length fourth. Rates on top and should go close. SAINT RICO (2) jumped from out wide and had a clear run, crossing to the lead and holding on for a placing when second (30.05) at Wentworth Park in a Mix 3/4 over 520m. Expected to feature again. SUNBURNT KEEPER (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at The Gardens over 400m behind Ella Knows (23.49) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. HURRY TUNCURRY (4) has top-three aspirations after placing last time.",
